{"id": "art-1402", "label": "Art. 1402", "title": "Art. 1402", "slug": "art-1402", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_796285724\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2223\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_796285724\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 140<sup>2</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1375593981\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2222\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1375593981\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\npoate crea comitete consultative formate din cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\n2 membri ai consiliului <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> îns&#259;rcinate cu <span\nclass=SpellE>desf&#259;&#351;urarea</span> de <span class=SpellE>investiga&#355;ii</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cu elaborarea de recomand&#259;ri pentru\nconsiliu, în domenii precum auditul, remunerarea administratorilor,\ndirectorilor, cenzorilor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> personalului sau\nnominalizarea de <span class=SpellE>candida&#355;i</span> pentru diferitele\nposturi de conducere. Comitetele vor înainta consiliului, în mod regulat,\nrapoarte asupra <span class=SpellE>activit&#259;&#355;ii</span> lor.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1956060635\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2221\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1956060635\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> un membru al\nfiec&#259;rui comitet creat în temeiul alin. (1) trebuie s&#259; fie\nadministrator neexecutiv independent. Comitetul de audit <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncel de remunerare sunt formate numai din administratori neexecutivi. Cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> un membru al comitetului de audit trebuie\ns&#259; <span class=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;</span> <span class=SpellE>experien&#355;&#259;</span>\nîn aplicarea principiilor contabile sau în audit financiar.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1930401495\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2220\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1930401495\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)[textul din Art. 140^2, alin. (3) din titlul III,\ncapitolul IV, <span class=SpellE>sectiunea</span> III, <span class=SpellE>subsectiunea</span>\nI a fost abrogat la 29-iun-2007 de </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>Art. I,\npunctul 19. din <span class=SpellE>Ordonanta</span> urgenta 82/2007</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>]</span></p>"}